Suzuki Motor Developing Fuel-Cell Scooter With UK's Intelligent Energy

-- B y   M a k i k o   K i t a m u r a
-- 
2011-03-09T05:14:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-09/suzuki-motor-developing-fuel-cell-scooter-with-uk-s-intelligent-energy.html
  Suzuki Motor Corp. (7269)  is developing a
fuel-cell scooter with the U.K.’s Intelligent Energy Holdings
Plc, said Ichizo Aoyama, the Japanese company’s head of research
and development told reporters today in Tokyo.
Suzuki plans to start selling the fuel-cell scooter in  Europe 
from 2015 for less than 8,000 euros, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Makiko Kitamura in Tokyo at 
